    "data": [
        {
            "title": "油尖警搗非法賭檔拘13人 包括4名通緝犯",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"被捕人士帶署調查。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d8b352b480315a85e1674e465f52b6ed/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031408425037465.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">被捕人士帶署調查。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>油尖警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查後，今日（14日）凌晨展開代號「逸影」（FLOWINGSHADE）的反罪惡及反三合會行動，突擊搜查上海街206號一單位，搗破一個懷疑非法賭檔。行動中，人員拘捕一名42歲姓黃本地男子，涉嫌「經營賭博場所」及「外出時沒有攜帶身份證明文件」，該名男子亦被發現為通緝人士。<br/>\n<br/>\n另外，人員亦在該單位以涉嫌「在賭博場所內賭博」拘捕8名本地男子、一名本地女子及3名非華裔男子，年齡介乎30至68歲。人員同時發現其中3名本地男子為通緝人士。<br/>\n<br/>\n行動中，人員檢獲五部釣魚機、一部讀卡機、一批遊戲卡及約3000元現金。所有被捕人現正被扣留調查。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058057/即時-港聞-油尖警搗非法賭檔拘13人-包括4名通緝犯",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 08:51:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "珍惜生命│西環消防局對開男子墮海 獲救昏迷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/430b63e6bc1b9c3545d14e3d73539f82/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031408362437334.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員到場調查。梁國峰攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> 西環堅彌地城新海旁，今（14日）早上7時28分，堅尼地城消防局對開，一名途人行經發現離岸對開50米，有一名人形物體背向天載浮載沉，走到消防局通知消防員及報警求助，消防員救起該名男子，他已陷昏迷，被送往中環碼頭上岸，再送往瑪麗醫院救治。警方正調查事主身份及墮海原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4136355/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"水警到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6111062d0f86eca00c580b94d6a65605/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_081141310_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        水警到場調查。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4136356/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1c4dee2143b138e2beb8bfde3bdcddbd/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_081141310_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4136357/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"西環堅彌地城新海旁男子墮海。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4653c04c212673038d72fe182bd1e415/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_081141310_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        西環堅彌地城新海旁男子墮海。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4136358/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a05f4cb0fd83d4f412b358433bc1bc53/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_081141310_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4136359/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99161f22db4fef565c00d6ad2dc57508/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_081912928.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> 防止自殺求助熱線：\n\n</p>\n<p>「情緒通」精神健康支援熱線：18111 \n\n</p>\n<p>香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222\n\n</p>\n<p>生命熱線： 2382 0000\n\n</p>\n<p>明愛向晴軒： 18288\n\n</p>\n<p>社會福利署： 2343 2255\n\n</p>\n<p>撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000\n\n</p>\n<p>東華三院芷若園： 18281\n\n</p>\n<p>醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350\n\n</p>\n<p>賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
