            "title": "天文台｜早晚有微雨及能見度頗低 下午短暫有陽光 最高氣溫約25度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f13722c27dbfe461a2985993a67e86e4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031407080263234.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股潮濕的偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港今早能見度頗低，港內的能見度在3000米以下。此外，一道雲帶覆蓋沿岸地區及南海北部。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲。早晚有一兩陣微雨及能見度頗低。下午短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約25度。吹和緩東風。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4136343/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/549aa13a14d82176b35ef43ad89e0402/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-03-13_at_11_03_12_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>展望明日日間溫暖，晚上至星期日北風增強，氣溫逐步下降。下週初早上最低氣溫在14度左右，日間乾燥。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058053/即時-港聞-天文台-早晚有微雨及能見度頗低-下午短暫有陽光-最高氣溫約25度",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 07:11:43",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "沙特職｜祖漢杜蘭夠弗  半場大「斯」殺",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"祖漢杜蘭加盟艾納斯已攻入6球。 REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/27dd098fcda7a1a836278ad4428558bb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031323422289037.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">祖漢杜蘭加盟艾納斯已攻入6球。 REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h4>足智彩球賽編號：FB8879<br/>\n艾納斯 VS 艾科魯特<br/>\nNow 633台周五凌晨4:00直播<br/>\n推介：半場入球大細[1.5]大</h4>\n<p>艾納斯在周中殺入亞冠精英盃8強，在聯賽卻仍須力爭前3，爭取來季亞冠精英盃參賽資格。射手祖漢杜蘭在周中梅開二度，重拾射門鞋，今晚於沙特職主場出擊可再度聯手C朗拿度數胡，對手艾科魯特失球數字高企之餘，近期卻入球增多，半場入球大細中位數1.5球的大盤逾兩倍應該有計。\n\n</p>\n<p>主隊艾納斯上周亞冠精英盃16強首回合時，在隊長C朗拿度缺陣下，前鋒祖漢杜蘭等人連番失機，結果要到次回合，才於主場以3:0輕取對手艾斯迪格拿，而前鋒祖漢杜蘭在得到C朗的支援下，重拾射門鞋，取得兩個入球，是其加盟後艾納斯個人第3次梅開二度。而C朗在該仗亦射入一記12碼，連續兩場取得入球，有這兩位數胡人物在陣，球隊的火力毋庸置疑。\n\n</p><h3>艾科魯特專入強隊波</h3>\n<p>沙特職的前3名才有來屆亞冠精英盃參賽資格，現時排第4位的艾納斯仍須積極搶分，今晚主場出擊中游的艾科魯特亦不容有失。球隊本身近6場作東射入17球，場均接近3球的火力，應足以贏下比賽，而近兩場皆在換邊前射入兩球，顯示球隊近期喜在主場搶攻。\n\n</p>\n<p>而客隊艾科魯特近期在主場取得5連勝，即使作客4連敗，從入球數字上卻明顯反映球隊正在佳態，尤其作客對希拉爾和伊蒂哈德兩場即使落敗，仍有力從這兩隊榜首球隊身上合共射入4球，而在該兩仗皆在半場已有4個總入球，縱使今場或難阻艾納斯取得最終勝利，卻大有機會攻破主隊大門。既然兩隊都有力爭取入球，半場入球大細中位數1.5球的「大」有2.08倍值博率高，取半場大盤相當合理。馬高\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058040/即時-體育-沙特職-祖漢杜蘭夠弗-半場大-斯-殺",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 07:06:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "意甲｜韋拉改革見成效  博熱拿亞「和主」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"韋拉領軍的熱拿亞近期防守穩健。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d4ab6639017d64e0fc34c449789b5949/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031323455033704.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">韋拉領軍的熱拿亞近期防守穩健。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h4>足智彩球賽編號：FB8882<br/>\n熱拿亞 VS 萊切<br/>\n香港時間周六凌晨3:45直播<br/>\n推介：半全場「和-主」</h4>\n<p>意甲另一隊和波專家之稱的熱拿亞，近期在主場的贏波能力有着明顯改善，近4場作東取得3勝1和的成績，這支由前阿仙奴名將韋拉執教的球隊今晚迎戰作客戰績差的萊切或佔上風；不過，近10場在換邊前錄得7次半場和兼本身只入一球，穩得太過分，半全場「和主」逾4倍分頭太吸引，不妨冷敲。\n\n</p>\n<p>熱拿亞的「穩」絕非浪得虛名，尤其主場合共3勝7和4負的成績中，和波次數佔了一半，這實在跟韋拉的穩固防守結構有關，值得留意的是，季內3次主場勝仗皆在近4場所得，證明球隊在穩守後，在進攻上有改善，面對作客14場輸9場的萊切應可佔優。\n\n</p><h3>熱拿亞近10場7次半場和</h3>\n<p>不過，熱拿亞近10場不但7次開半場和，本身更極少在上半場入波，合計之下「和主」最正路之餘，更有逾4倍的不俗分頭，值得一試。馬高\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058041/即時-體育-意甲-韋拉改革見成效-博熱拿亞-和主",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-14 07:06:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "「最索經理人」林寶玉：要學精啲 自爆曾誤墮網上賣華仔飛陷阱丨獨家",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"「最索經理人」林寶玉：要學精啲 自爆曾誤墮網上賣華仔飛陷阱。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9b07605a6a7facecde22c461cf3c58e5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031403003145021.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">「最索經理人」林寶玉：要學精啲 自爆曾誤墮網上賣華仔飛陷阱。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>「最索經理人」林寶玉有勇有謀，年前成功捧起藝人薛影儀，由香港紅到大馬。不過，林寶玉提醒自己於新的一年要學精啲，原來去年被呃兩次，繼網購1折商務機票中招後，再幫朋友撲劉德華個唱門票，誤墮網上炒飛陷阱，遭連環被騙損失2萬元，惜追究無門。 採訪：方騫平 場地：the market @hotel icon\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉小事胡塗。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eddbc2e3f5974f4500b4c0dd04fe1e1a/2025-03/23012025_010.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉小事胡塗。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉想搵金主開戲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0aa8fb46c1d3ca447b2d88557393cab6/2025-03/23012025_004.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉想搵金主開戲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉好有人緣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f23d42042e069ed3bb0bcc3edaf43bc/2025-03/23012025_012.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉好有人緣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉有唔少追求者。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba26e97f1b06c3d5a28a0c89b5db437b/2025-03/23012025_023.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉有唔少追求者。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"寶玉笑容甜美。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/40f8439a5e6621a991603357db84dc70/2025-03/23012025_025.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶玉笑容甜美。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"寶玉好易受騙。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/263eb0c8b9d56d55c8419c13a23a8d17/2025-03/23012025_030.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶玉好易受騙。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"太忙旳寶玉甚少留意時事新聞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3b6a2121b6a8a64b3cbb92678a9d9cc/2025-03/23012025_034.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        太忙旳寶玉甚少留意時事新聞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>「遠離」薛影儀年半的林寶玉事業走得更遠，除經營美容生意外，年初更成立娛樂公司，接洽經理人、電影、製作等工作。對於阿儀多次出言攻擊「咬住」她唔放，去年兩人活動中聚頭，又當眾大鬧寶玉是「死八婆」！難得林寶玉唔嬲反笑。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿儀開口埋口都會主動提及前經理人林寶玉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af05ca73fa03604f99335b660c5d5a85/2025-03/01_1_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿儀開口埋口都會主動提及前經理人林寶玉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉成立娛樂公司搞埋製作，活動中和冼靖峰碰頭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f9fb371092bdc578c68decbd0a793da4/2025-03/thumbnail_7__2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉成立娛樂公司搞埋製作，活動中和冼靖峰碰頭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"去年10月林寶玉獲邀為「巴黎時裝周」擔任天橋模特兒。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2f0684bdfe67c5bc346d95670c5de8a3/2025-03/10__1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        去年10月林寶玉獲邀為「巴黎時裝周」擔任天橋模特兒。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"活動中「波霸」葉子楣相遇。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/041102d494a9a9d5d3c233f7a3032c6c/2025-03/thumbnail_1__3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        活動中「波霸」葉子楣相遇。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉抽空和黃守東做善事。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4c0b74e42801feb519746ad77da30dc/2025-03/_1_7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉抽空和黃守東做善事。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"寶玉幫灣仔區獨居長者搬梳化。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e49066eb9685c751fc6c57cd5c20197/2025-03/_3_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶玉幫灣仔區獨居長者搬梳化。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>跟阿儀3年緣份</strong>\n</p>\n<p>林寶玉指阿儀的舉動難以理解：「佢每次鬧完我，都會禮貌地邀請我睇返，只能話，每個人表達愛意嘅方法都唔同，阿儀表達形式別樹一格，而且我覺得喺佢心目中，我份量好高，所以成日會記掛住我。(咁你點回應佢？)我零回覆，亦冇興趣睇，睇完都唔知有乜好講。」林寶玉不得不承認和阿儀好有緣份：「記得我哋第一年合作時，睇相話我哋都有一粒名氣聲，碰埋成就咗阿儀『黃金3年』。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"薛影儀、林寶玉曾共事3年。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d1a04bdc1905adbd531b1edeaf1bd66/2025-03/Screenshot_20220908_202638_com_instagram_android_edit_69829107812781.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        薛影儀、林寶玉曾共事3年。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當年阿儀人氣急升。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d2a5951fcc730e02a286e13e83ee7918/2025-03/IMG-20220626-WA0276_-_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當年阿儀人氣急升。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿儀仲出歌拍MV。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5a2efb9455f7e147cca9e22b2f1d6ce/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2023-06-06_at_10_12_52.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿儀仲出歌拍MV。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉、薛影儀有過經歷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/110d84737ecad838c98ce0c056c9adf9/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2023-06-06_at_16_59_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉、薛影儀有過經歷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>近日林寶玉成立娛樂公司，她不排除投放資金開戲，坦言如果經濟許可，都想做返多些幕前，尤其擺脫做花瓶，想試下做癲婆。正因工作太忙，感情生活一片空白，追問索爆林寶玉可有被富商追求？她冇否定，笑說：「我唔知點界定係富商？喺我眼中只要有上進心，未來發展及賺錢空間好大。不過，𠵱家最多聽到追求者嗰句係『你太忙、太強唔知點追你。』」林寶玉提醒自己新一年除要放慢腳步外更要醒目些：「我好少睇新聞，去年網購1折商務機票中招，被呃$15000。」之後她心急幫朋友撲劉德華個唱門票，再誤墮網上炒飛陷阱：「我仲以為買家係信得過嘅愛心媽媽，所以由最初買2張加碼到8張，仲落咗$4000訂金，點知約好交收後就失聯…」她自嘲道：「唉！我咁好呃，唯一好彩冇畀人呃咗去KK園區。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"去年劉德華紅館個唱一票難求。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14232ec344b9b2ddf2c07432c74e62fd/2025-03/0101_3_IMG_0623_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        去年劉德華紅館個唱一票難求。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"被封為「最索經理人」的林寶玉有腦有身材。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a30ca94fdd592fec042806585c22495b/2025-03/IMG_1571.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被封為「最索經理人」的林寶玉有腦有身材。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"寶玉性感迷人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/47757c0944713933b17d6a0cc3e0c31e/2025-03/FB_IMG_1686144145509.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶玉性感迷人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"發揮女強人本色常外出工幹。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c0ff7680fa502b99913de562e7a0c60e/2025-03/thumbnail_5__3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        發揮女強人本色常外出工幹。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"林寶玉有時間都陪下家人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d0c6aea917d4b5916f23331297e4391/2025-03/thumbnail_3__1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林寶玉有時間都陪下家人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
